&lt;p id="zerky7"&gt;Alternatively, if you prefer your console to come with its disc drive (instead of having to potentially add one later), you can get a &lt;strong&gt;disc-ready PS5&lt;/strong&gt; for $424 (regularly $499) at &lt;a href="https://howl.link/a96z6zpacc2ax"&gt;Best Buy&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href="https://goto.walmart.com/c/482924/565706/9383?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.walmart.com%2Fip%2FSony-PlayStation-5-PS5-Disc-Console-Slim%2F5113183756&amp;amp;sharedid=theverge.com" rel="sponsored nofollow noopener" target="_blank"&gt;Walmart&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href="https://go.redirectingat.com?id=66960X1514734&amp;amp;xs=1&amp;amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Fdirect.playstation.com%2Fen-us%2Fbuy-consoles%2Fplaystation5-console-model-group-slim&amp;amp;referrer=theverge.com&amp;amp;sref=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theverge.com%2F2024%2F11%2F30%2F24308967%2Fblack-friday-2024-playstation-5-ps5-slim-digital-edition-disc-cyber-monday" rel="sponsored nofollow noopener" target="_blank"&gt;PlayStation Direct&lt;/a&gt;, and &lt;a href="https://www.amazon.com/PlayStation%C2%AE5-Digital-slim-PlayStation-5/dp/B0DJHF6Q9Z?th=1&amp;amp;tag=theverge02-20" rel="sponsored nofollow noopener" target="_blank"&gt;Amazon&lt;/a&gt; (in that same &lt;em&gt;Fortnite&lt;/em&gt; bundle). &lt;a href="https://go.redirectingat.com?id=66960X1514734&amp;amp;xs=1&amp;amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Fdirect.playstation.com%2Fen-us%2F&amp;amp;referrer=theverge.com&amp;amp;sref=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theverge.com%2F2024%2F11%2F30%2F24308967%2Fblack-friday-2024-playstation-5-ps5-slim-digital-edition-disc-cyber-monday" rel="sponsored nofollow noopener" target="_blank"&gt;A...&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
